
                                            The incident occurred under the Okavango Road Bridge on Friday morning.
                                         CAPE TOWN – A woman has been killed in a suspected hit-and-run the N1 highway. The incident occurred under the Okavango Road Bridge pn Friday morning. Traffic services' Richard Coleman said: “We have the left lane closed due to a hit-and-run accident. An adult female was fatally injured during this incident.” Coleman adds a police investigation is underway. (Edited by Shimoney Regter)